snippet.title: [QUAKE] RUBICON 2 (Nightmare difficulty, 100% Kills & Secrets)
snippet.description:
Playthrough of Rubicon 2 episode for the first Quake game. Completed on nightmare difficulty, with 100% kills and secrets achieved on every level.

Rubicon 2: http://celephais.net/levels/rubicon2/

Music: "I Desensitize", "Compass", "Uplift" and "Reprogram" by Neurotech
https://neurotech.bandcamp.com/

Quake by id Software
https://www.idsoftware.com
